---

<PageLayout
  title="Free AI Training for Nonprofits: Tools, Grants & Resources (2025 Guide)"
  description="Complete guide to free AI training and resources for nonprofits. Access $10K+/month in grants, free AI tools, training programs, and implementation guides designed specifically for nonprofit organizations."
  showHeader={true}
  showCTA={false}
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 to-purple-900 text-white py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-600/20 backdrop-blur-sm px-6 py-3 rounded-full mb-8 border border-green-400/30">
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold">ðŸŽ¯ Complete Resource Guide for Nonprofit AI Adoption</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight">
        Free AI Training & Tools<br/>
        <span class="text-green-400">for Nonprofits</span><br/>
        Save 30+ Hours/Month
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 mb-12 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        While 78% of nonprofits struggle with limited resources, the ones using AI
        are <span class="font-bold text-yellow-300">saving 30+ hours monthly</span> and accessing
        <span class="font-bold text-yellow-300">$10,000+/month in free tools</span>.
        Here's your complete guide.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
