      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        {implementationSteps.map(step => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
                {step.step}
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">{step.title}</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              {step.tasks.map(task => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <Icon name="check" class="text-green-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" size="sm" />
                  <span class="text-gray-700">{task}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Use Cases Section -->
  <Section background="white" padding="xl">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">
        Real AI Applications <span class="text-orange-600">by Department</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 text-lg mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Specific ways nonprofits are using AI today with time savings data
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {commonUseCases.map(useCase => (
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-yellow-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-orange-200">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">{useCase.area}</h3>
              <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
                {useCase.savings}
              </span>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              {useCase.applications.map(app => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-orange-500 mt-1">â†’</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-700 text-sm">{app}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Grants Section -->
  <Section background="cream" padding="xl">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">
        AI Implementation Grants <span class="text-green-600">for Nonprofits</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 text-lg mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Funding specifically available for nonprofits adopting AI technology
      </p>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-gray-100 border-b border-gray-200">
              <th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Grant Program</th>
              <th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Amount</th>
              <th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Deadline</th>
              <th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Focus Area</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {grants.map((grant, index) => (
              <tr class={`border-b border-gray-200 ${index % 2 === 0 ? 'bg-white' : 'bg-gray-50'}`}>
                <td class="p-4">
                  <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">{grant.name}</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">{grant.eligibility}</div>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4 font-bold text-green-600">{grant.amount}</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-gray-700">{grant.deadline}</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-gray-700 text-sm">{grant.focus}</td>
              </tr>
            ))}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-green-100 rounded-xl border border-green-200">
        <p class="text-green-900 font-semibold mb-2">ðŸŽ¯ Grant Application Tip:</p>
        <p class="text-green-800">
          Focus your application on measurable impact metrics. Funders want to see how AI will
