          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="font-bold">ROI:</span> 25 hours/month saved = $50K annual value,
            $240K additional funding, total impact: $290K with $0 tool cost.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-sm">
            "AI didn't replace our grant writerâ€”it made her 3x more effective. She now
            manages relationships instead of formatting documents."
            <span class="block mt-2 font-semibold">- Director of Development</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <Section background="gradient" padding="xl">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center text-white">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
